    <h2>Fonts</h2>
        <p>
        	Font is the set of letters that have similar properties. Usually one can describe a font by using 
        	shape, style, and size. Font sample defines the special details of the font, for example the 
        	thickness of the font. Style defines whether the font is slanted. Size defines the size of the font.
        </P>

